{"id":"chatbot_basic_001","category":"basic","title":"极短能力询问","difficulty":"easy","tags":["short-input","capability","zh"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"你能做什么？别太长。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"markdown","behavior":"用简短中文说明对话、总结、整理、格式化等能力，不夸大未接入能力。"},"must_include":["总结"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_002","category":"basic","title":"杂乱会议记录整理","difficulty":"medium","tags":["summary","messy-input","markdown"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"下面这个帮我整理一下：今天说了上线时间可能推迟，设计稿还没最终确认，小王负责接口，小李说数据字段还差两个，周五再碰一次。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"markdown","behavior":"将杂乱内容整理为事项、负责人、风险和下次动作。"},"must_include":["风险"],"must_include_any":[["负责人","负责","分工"]],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_003","category":"basic","title":"表格输出预算比较","difficulty":"medium","tags":["table","comparison","format"],"evaluation_type":"automatic","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"把三个方案做成表格：A方案便宜但慢，B方案贵但稳定，C方案中等价格但是要多沟通。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"table","behavior":"用 Markdown 表格比较三个方案的成本、优点、缺点和适用情况。"},"must_include":["|","A方案","B方案","C方案"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":false}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_004","category":"basic","title":"严格 JSON 输出","difficulty":"medium","tags":["json","format","structured-output"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"只输出JSON，字段有title、priority、next_actions。内容：客户催上线，接口还没验收，今天必须确认负责人。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"json","behavior":"只输出合法 JSON，包含 title、priority、next_actions，不额外解释。"},"must_include":["title","priority","next_actions"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_005","category":"basic","title":"中英混合但中文回复","difficulty":"easy","tags":["zh-required","mixed-language"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Please explain API rate limit，用中文，像给新人讲。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"markdown","behavior":"用中文解释 API rate limit 的含义、影响和简单处理方式。"},"must_include":["API","限制"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_006","category":"basic","title":"一句话改写","difficulty":"easy","tags":["rewrite","concise"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"把这句话改正式一点：这个东西老是坏，客户很烦。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"plain","behavior":"将口语表达改写为正式、克制、适合工作沟通的中文句子。"},"must_include":[],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_007","category":"basic","title":"提取待办事项","difficulty":"medium","tags":["todo","extraction","messy-input"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"帮我提待办：明天先问财务发票状态，那个合同让法务再看一眼，还有别忘了把测试账号发给产品。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"markdown","behavior":"提取清晰待办项，尽量保留对象和动作。"},"must_include":["财务","法务","测试账号"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_008","category":"basic","title":"要求 Markdown 大纲","difficulty":"easy","tags":["markdown","outline"],"evaluation_type":"automatic","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"给我一个学习 FastAPI 的三天计划，用Markdown。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"markdown","behavior":"输出三天学习计划，包含每天主题和任务。"},"must_include":["第一天","第二天","第三天"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":false}
