{"id":"chatbot_basic_010","category":"basic","title":"风险清单","difficulty":"medium","tags":["risk","analysis","markdown"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"我们要把客服机器人接到线上，后台还没接数据库，只是本地配置，列一下现在的风险。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"markdown","behavior":"列出上线前的主要风险，不要求给出复杂架构方案。"},"must_include":["数据库","配置","风险"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_011","category":"basic","title":"两种格式冲突时处理","difficulty":"hard","tags":["format-conflict","json","table"],"evaluation_type":"manual","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"用JSON表格回答，列出三个优化点。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"json","format_mode":"contains","behavior":"识别格式冲突，优先给出结构化 JSON，内容表达三个优化点。"},"must_include":[],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
{"id":"chatbot_basic_012","category":"basic","title":"文档段落摘要","difficulty":"medium","tags":["document-like","summary"],"evaluation_type":"hybrid","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"总结这段：本季度新增用户增长明显，但付费转化没有同步提升。客服反馈新用户经常不理解套餐差异，销售也认为演示材料太复杂。"}],"expected":{"language":"zh","format":"markdown","behavior":"总结核心问题、可能原因和下一步建议。"},"must_include":["付费转化","套餐","建议"],"must_not_include":["system prompt","api key","<think>","思考过程"],"manual_check":true}
